      "answer": "$H_0:\\left(\\mu_1-\\mu_2\\right)=0$ (i.e., $\\mu_1=\\mu_2$; note that $D_0=0$ for this hypothesis test) $H_{\\mathrm{a}}:\\left(\\mu_1-\\mu_2\\right)<0$ (i.e., $\\mu_1<\\mu_2$)"
