    {
      "query": "Specify the test statistic formula and the rejection region for the hypothesis test.",
      "answer": "Test statistic: $z=\\frac{\\left(\\bar{x}_1-\\bar{x}_2\\right)-D_0}{\\sigma_{\\left(\\bar{x}_1-\\bar{x}_2\\right)}}=\\frac{\\left(\\bar{x}_1-\\bar{x}_2\\right)-0}{\\sigma_{\\left(\\bar{x}_1-\\bar{x}_2\\right)}}$ Rejection region: $z<-z_{.05}=-1.645$ (see Figure 8.3)"
