      "answer": "$z=\\frac{\\left(\\bar{x}_1-\\bar{x}_2\\right)-0}{\\sigma_{\\left(\\bar{x}_1-\\bar{x}_2\\right)}}=\\frac{(16,596-17,236)}{\\sqrt{\\frac{\\sigma_1^2}{n_1}+\\frac{\\sigma_2^2}{n_2}}} \\approx \\frac{-640}{\\sqrt{\\frac{s_1^2}{n_1}+\\frac{s_2^2}{n_2}}}=\\frac{-640}{\\sqrt{\\frac{(1,981)^2}{50}+\\frac{(1,974)^2}{50}}}=\\frac{-640}{396}=-1.62$"
